# Environment Variables Template

# TMDb API Key (Required)
# Get yours at: https://www.themoviedb.org/settings/api
TMDB_API_KEY=your_tmdb_api_key_here

# Watchmode API Key (Optional)
# Get yours at: https://api.watchmode.com/
# Note: TMDb provides basic streaming info for free
WATCHMODE_API_KEY=your_watchmode_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with actual API keys
# 3. NEVER commit .env to git (it's always in .gitignore!)
# 4. For Netlify/Vercel/whateverelse: Add these as environment variables in their respective dashboards